resolution: Changed workflow path filters so plugin markdown changes on main run functional CI while docs markdown still routes through docs workflow.
expected_result: Plugin markdown edits are not skipped by all functional validation on push.
actual_result: "CI workflow now uses paths with plugins/** re-inclusion; workflow contract, docs gates, and coverage passed."
